{"tid":766631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿叔隻手真係好污糟..........","createTime":"2018-08-03T17:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T17:45:40.000Z","uid":195479,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ba19c2ecbeb65f52ce547f186d44d364e109e5","tid":766631,"uid":195479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:41:13.000Z","msg":"屌 阿叔係咪唔撚識得洗手<br />\n好撚多阿叔都好撚污糟<br />\n用手抹鼻涕 周圍hi<br />\n隨地吐痰<br />\n係廁所永遠都見到佢地 屙完篤尿 拉完褲鏈就拍拍囉柚直接走 <br />\n手都唔撚洗一下<br />\n有d就開個水龍頭 象徵式沖一下就走 隻手掂到d水唔夠0. 1秒就縮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔敢想像廁所個手柄幾污糟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/013642_5876c0a948500b0e757001860a801aa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F013642_5876c0a948500b0e757001860a801aa9.png&h=92b2ec65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6075838ac6412f25d3c433470dcc9e955771c10","tid":766631,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"郭峰手臂咁撚粗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e085ab97782b58103a11a265e4d7c6111518a3","tid":766631,"uid":195479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6075838ac6412f25d3c433470dcc9e955771c10","tid":766631,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"郭峰手臂咁撚粗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"明顯右手揸慣槍<br />\n個海報都講埋<br />\n仲問<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}